Plot: A master thief, fresh out of prison after 15 years, assumes the identity of a dead sheriff in Banshee, PA after tracking down the woman he loves, while trying to avoid detection from her father, a Ukrainian mobster that is looking for the two is them in order to kill them for double crossing him.
Title: Banshee Origins
Actors: Frankie Faison, Antony Starr, Ivana Milicevic, Ulrich Thomsen
